{"tid":696670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺同窮人做朋友好難頂","createTime":"2018-06-10T10:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T05:45:24.000Z","uid":56508,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f81995d8a6d20ab78faaca863cb6a123802335ba","tid":696670,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"我唔係話我好有錢 只不過係正常人 普通人<br />\n都無睇唔起比自己窮既朋友<br />\n<br />\n但係多年來 總結既係同稍為屋企無咁有錢既人做朋友有啲麻煩<br />\n<br />\n有時會單單打打話唔當佢係朋友 唔約佢<br />\n但係約親佢十次有九次都話返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n到真係出黎 佢又嫌食嘢貴 <br />\n諗住同佢食平啲 食下M記同譚仔又嫌cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時自己買咗樣都叫幾貴既嘢開心share下<br />\n又會串你有錢喇 用好嘢 問我幾時送俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最難頂係日日係到怨天怨地 話自己失敗係因為窮 <br />\n例如做嘢唔如意係因為人地睇佢唔起<br />\n聽佢呻 又話我唔明 唔會理解佢喎"},{"pid":"2ba4f9bd21a74bd5df36cf71e5023ecab6e9bbe6","tid":696670,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"無咩緊要野都唔好聯絡。"},{"pid":"8748d42b55e40e148478d9809f43a6cfb91f2114","tid":696670,"uid":56508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ba4f9bd21a74bd5df36cf71e5023ecab6e9bbe6","tid":696670,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"無咩緊要野都唔好聯絡。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"以前我嘅心態係話晒舊時都叫做同學一場<br />\n有時都會問候下佢嘅<br />\n<br />\n但係今時今日覺得佢真係好難頂<br />\n同佢講野有時仲要俾佢單單打打"},{"pid":"4d9e411a01367e9c261d5956b935225fd14bdfc2","tid":696670,"uid":17920,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"你個朋友窮得閪<br />\n<br />\n唔好拖埋其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ad6dc95e576ce6576661bca2cfb7c6651303cf","tid":696670,"uid":68598,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"你個朋友窮得黎仲要自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\